      • switchProjects

        public void switchProjects(int newProjectID,
                           ActionButtonsBox actionButtonsBox)
        Switch from one project to another.

        (1)copy the current timeStamp and timeStampCursor into the current Project record

        (2)retrieve the timeStamp and timeStampCursor from the new Project

        (4)save the current Project record to the database

        (3)set 'currentProject' to be the new project

        (4)the calling method must refresh the display

        Parameters:
        newProjectID - the ID of the project to switch to
        actionButtonsBox - the actionButtonsBox which has invoked the switch (and which knows the buttonState of the current project)
